**This is a MULTI-REPO WORKSPACE, not a single project.** The repos below are cloned as subdirectories. Each repo has its own CLAUDE.md with repo-specific build commands, test runners, and lint configs. This file contains ONLY cross-repo context: relationships, codenames, deploy order, and tribal knowledge. Do not add repo-specific information here.

> **Before any `git` command, verify your working directory.** Each repo in this workspace has its own git history. Run `pwd` before `git status`, `git add`, `git commit`, `git push`, or any destructive git operation — a commit in the wrong repo is a real source of bugs, not a hypothetical one.

The repo registry is in `repos.json`. Run `make setup` to clone all repos.

